&lt;p&gt;The schedule for this position is:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Tuesday-Saturday with the hours being: three shifts 11am-7pm and two shifts 9am-5pm in your time zone&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
