&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Prioritize and manage individual members along the Twin journey to reversal and self-care management&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Deliver remote coaching via apps, video conferencing, and the Twin Health electronic system&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Engage and activate members to set goals, manage their care, and stay motivated on their journey to self efficacy&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Motivate, coach, and provide exceptional service and support to your members

